script:
1). You wouldn't know Bill's last name, would you?
Yes, it's Johnson. 
I will know it.
No, I couldn't.
2). Did Jonah do this credit report?
No he won't.
Yes, he did it. 
No he hasn't.
3). Have you booked the hotel rooms yet?
Yes, I had done it.
I finished the book yesterday.
No, I'll do it right away.
